title: Emirates Talent Association launches Innovation Award sponsored by DEWA (Dubai Electricity and Water Authority)
text: ( Source : Dubai Electricity and Water Authority ) Wed, 21 Oct 2015 The Emirates Talent Association is inviting UAE National students of 12 to 18 years of age, to apply for the international IQ Test , to measure their intelligence quotient
